---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

import Container from "../../components/container.astro";
import JobApplicationForm from "../../components/jobapplicationform.astro";
---

<Layout title="Career">
  <Container>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Front-end Developer</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <div class="text-slate-700">
        <!-- <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl text-gray-800">Contact Nerd's House</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500 mt-3">
          Have something to say? We are here to help. Fill up the form or send
          email or call phone.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5"></div> -->

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          Nerd's House is looking for HTML/CSS ninjas with WordPress theme
          development experience.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          The following qualities will help you to become a nerd.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc text-sm font-light pl-8 mb-4">
          <li>
            Strong development expertise using core tools HTML5, CSS3,
            JavaScript, and PHP
          </li>
          <li>
            Experience working with WordPress, building custom WordPress themes
            and/or plugins, and configuring content using custom fields
          </li>
          <li>Experience using CSS Grid, CSS Flexbox</li>
          <li>Experience using Advanced Custom Fields</li>
          <li>Basic understanding of JS Frameworks like React and Angular</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Why Nerd's House?</h2>

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          We have crafted our own culture and traditions in the past decade and
          the highlights are:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc text-sm font-light pl-8 mb-4">
          <li>International client exposure</li>
          <li>Best employee benefits in the industry</li>
          <li>Performance appraisal twice a year</li>
          <li>Availability of remote work option</li>
          <li>Full stacked pantry in office</li>
          <li>Absence of leave restraints</li>
          <li>No micro-management</li>
          <li>Frequent outings and pizza parties</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mb-4 text-sm">
          So if you are looking for a fairyland to spread your wings without
          being stifled by the constraints of the usual corporate culture look
          no further. We are happy to welcome you to our family.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <JobApplicationForm />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a
        href="/career"
        class="bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >‚Üê Back to Career</a
      >
    </div> 
  </Container>
</Layout>
